<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The method addTranslation() in Zend_Translate_Adapter contains a bug at the end of the method which overwrites the previous locale.
It checks whether the original locale is set with:</p>

<p>isset($translate[$originate])</p>

<p>However this is never true since the variable $translate does not exist. It should rather be</p>

<p>isset($this-&gt;_translate[$originate])</p>

<p>Otherwise when performing a directory scan the locale will be set to the last one found during the scan.</p>

    </div>
</div>

